plugins.name: SQL Syntax Highlighter
plugins.description: Advanced SQL syntax highlighting with support for multiple SQL dialects including PostgreSQL, MySQL, SQLite, and Oracle. Features include keyword completion, error highlighting, and theme customization.
plugins.author: FXDB Team

plugins.name: MongoDB Connector
plugins.description: Connect to MongoDB databases. Browse collections, execute queries using MongoDB query language, and manage documents with a visual interface.
plugins.author: FXDB Team

plugins.name: Redis Connector
plugins.description: Connect to Redis key-value stores. Browse keys, view values, execute Redis commands, and monitor real-time data changes.
plugins.author: FXDB Team

plugins.name: Apache Cassandra Connector
plugins.description: Connect to Apache Cassandra clusters. Execute CQL queries, manage keyspaces and tables, and monitor cluster health.
plugins.author: FXDB Team

plugins.name: Data Export Tools
plugins.description: Export query results and table data to various formats including CSV, Excel, JSON, XML, and SQL INSERT statements.
plugins.author: FXDB Team

plugins.name: Schema Visualizer
plugins.description: Generate ER diagrams and visualize database schema relationships. Supports automatic layout, export to PNG/SVG, and interactive navigation.
plugins.author: FXDB Team

plugins.name: Query History Manager
plugins.description: Track and manage SQL query history. Search past queries, bookmark favorites, and analyze query execution statistics.
plugins.author: FXDB Team

plugins.name: Dark Theme Pack
plugins.description: Additional dark themes for the FXDB interface including Dracula, Nord, One Dark, and Monokai color schemes.
plugins.author: FXDB Team
